<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Gelan Eagles - U13 & U15 Soccer Club</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-gray-100">
    <header class="bg-green-600 text-white">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-6">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-futbol text-4xl mr-4"></i>
                    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">Gelan Eagles</h1>
                </div>
                <nav>
                    <ul class="flex space-x-4">
                        <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-yellow-300 transition duration-300">Home</a></li>
                        <li><a href="//about" class="hover:text-yellow-300 transition duration-300">About</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/teams" class="hover:text-yellow-300 transition duration-300">Teams</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/contact" class="hover:text-yellow-300 transition duration-300">Contact</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="bg-green-500 text-white py-20">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Join the Gelan Eagles and Soar to New Heights!</h2>
                <p class="text-xl mb-8">Develop your soccer skills, make friends, and have fun with our U13 and U15 teams.</p>
                <a href="/contact#tryout" class="bg-yellow-400 text-green-800 font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-full hover:bg-yellow-300 transition duration-300">Join Now</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="py-16">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300">
                        <i class="fas fa-trophy text-4xl text-green-600 mb-4"></i>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Skilled Coaches</h3>
                        <p>Learn from experienced coaches dedicated to developing young talent.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300">
                        <i class="fas fa-users text-4xl text-green-600 mb-4"></i>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Team Spirit</h3>
                        <p>Build lasting friendships and develop strong teamwork skills.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300">
                        <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt text-4xl text-green-600 mb-4"></i>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Regular Matches</h3>
                        <p>Participate in exciting matches and tournaments throughout the season.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="bg-green-100 py-16">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Our Teams</h2>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
                        <img src="u13.jpg" alt="U13 Team" class="w-full h-48 object-cover">
                        <div class="p-6">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">U13 Team</h3>
                            <p>Our U13 team focuses on developing fundamental skills and fostering a love for the game.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
                        <img src="u15.jpg" alt="U15 Team" class="w-full h-48 object-cover">
                        <div class="p-6">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">U15 Team</h3>
                            <p>The U15 team builds on core skills and introduces more advanced tactics and gameplay.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="py-16">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Join the Gelan Eagles Family</h2>
                <p class="text-xl mb-8">Ready to take your soccer skills to the next level? Contact us to learn more about joining our U13 or U15 teams!</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="bg-green-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-full hover:bg-green-500 transition duration-300">Contact Us</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-green-800 text-white py-8">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
            <p>&copy; 2023 Gelan Eagles Soccer Club. All rights reserved.</p>
            <div class="mt-4">
                <a href="#" class="text-2xl mx-2 hover:text-yellow-300 transition duration-300"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a>
                <a href="#" class="text-2xl mx-2 hover:text-yellow-300 transition duration-300"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                <a href="#" class="text-2xl mx-2 hover:text-yellow-300 transition duration-300"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>